Definition: a hypocritical display of sorrow
Example: false or insincere weeping; the secretaries wept crocodile tears over the manager's dilemma; politicians shed crocodile tears over the plight of the unemployed
Synonyms: hypocrisy, a, hypocritical, display, of, sorrow, false, or, insincere, weeping, the, secretaries, wept, crocodile, tears, over, manager, s, dilemma, politicians, shed, plight, unemployed
Category: noun.communication
